06:03.080 --> 06:06.721
- What's a fuck-ass?
- [Dad laughs]

06:09.720 --> 06:11.768
[knock at door]

06:11.880 --> 06:13.962
[softly] Hi.

06:14.360 --> 06:16.567
I'm reading. Get out.

06:20.760 --> 06:22.842
Where do you go at night?

06:23.840 --> 06:25.922
Will you get out of my room?

06:26.000 --> 06:27.843
Did you toilet-paper the Johnsons'?

06:27.920 --> 06:30.764
- You came to ask me that?
- No.

06:31.920 --> 06:34.446
I stopped rolling houses in sixth grade.

06:34.560 --> 06:38.770
What happened to my son?
I don't recognise this person.

06:38.880 --> 06:41.281
You start taking the goddamn pills!

06:49.440 --> 06:51.727
[Door slams]

06:51.800 --> 06:53.928
Bitch.

07:02.080 --> 07:04.845
Our son just called me a bitch.

07:07.760 --> 07:09.808
You're not a bitch.

07:11.480 --> 07:14.802
You're bitching, but you're not a bitch.

07:18.240 --> 07:20.322
[Sighs]

07:52.760 --> 07:55.445
<i>I</i> want <i>to</i> be a president who <i>makes</i> sure

07:55.560 --> 07:59.645
<i>we never again do business
with a Panamanian dictator.</i>

07:59.720 --> 08:03.486
<i>- That we never again funnel aid...
- Dukakis.</i>

08:03.560 --> 08:06.609
- Son of a bitch.
- Panama is friendly.

08:06.680 --> 08:09.889
<i>- I talked to Panama's president...</i>
- <i>Tell</i> him, <i>George!</i>

08:10.000 --> 08:12.571
<i>...about cleaning up their money-laundering.</i>

08:12.720 --> 08:16.327
<i>Mr. Noriega was there, but there was no evidence...</i>

08:16.400 --> 08:20.689
[clock chimes]

08:22.040 --> 08:24.327
[ghostly voice] Wake up.

08:47.560 --> 08:50.245
<i>I've been watching you.</i>

09:16.040 --> 09:18.566
<i>Come closer.</i>

09:28.240 --> 09:30.322
Closer.

09:53.960 --> 09:56.008
28 days,

09:57.320 --> 09:59.402
six hours,

09:59.720 --> 10:01.802
42 minutes,

10:02.960 --> 10:05.088
12 seconds.

10:10.600 --> 10:15.288
That is when the world will end.

10:16.200 --> 10:18.328
Why?

10:18.960 --> 10:21.008
