10:33.960 --> 10:36.042
[car drives off]

10:41.560 --> 10:43.642
[sighs]

10:49.840 --> 10:52.081
[rumbling and crashing]

10:55.160 --> 10:57.242
[glass shatters]

10:58.640 --> 11:00.768
[alarm]

11:01.400 --> 11:03.607
[panting]

11:20.200 --> 11:21.725
Son?

11:21.800 --> 11:24.406
Son? Donnie Darko?

11:24.520 --> 11:26.568
Donnie Darko?

11:26.640 --> 11:29.086
- What's going on?
- Who is it?

11:29.160 --> 11:33.324
It's Eddie Darko's kid.
I'm sorry about this. He's a local kid.

11:34.400 --> 11:38.007
- Guess he was sleep-golfing.
- [Both laugh]

11:38.080 --> 11:40.731
Watch out for that drool spot.

11:42.840 --> 11:44.922
Are you all right, son?

11:51.280 --> 11:55.205
Let's stay off the links at night, OK?

11:55.280 --> 11:59.729
I'm sorry, Dr. Fisher. It won't happen again.

12:01.000 --> 12:03.810
- I hate kids.
- Let's golf.

12:03.920 --> 12:06.002
[Sirens]

12:11.400 --> 12:14.131
[girl] Donnie! Donnie! Donnie!

12:14.240 --> 12:16.368
What happened to your house?

12:18.680 --> 12:22.241
- No-one's allowed through...
- This is my house!

12:24.120 --> 12:26.202
He's OK.

12:28.040 --> 12:30.771
[Girl] Donnie, we know you're OK!

12:30.840 --> 12:35.607
[Reporter] Channel 6 News.
We have just arrived on the scene...

12:50.760 --> 12:53.411
Wait a minute. Here's your brother.

12:53.480 --> 12:56.211
- Oh!
- It fell in your room.

12:56.280 --> 12:59.170
Watch yourself down there!

13:16.480 --> 13:20.929
Mrs. Darko? I'm Bob Garland. I'm with the FAA.

13:21.000 --> 13:23.924
- You're what?
- I'm with the FAA.

13:24.000 --> 13:26.890
We'd like to speak
to you and Mr. Darko privately.

13:27.000 --> 13:29.207
- In private?
- Please.

13:30.640 --> 13:32.722
All right.

13:47.840 --> 13:49.968
And... here.

13:50.040 --> 13:52.202
- You got it.
- OK.

13:52.280 --> 13:56.410
We have arranged for you
to stay at a hotel, get some sleep.

13:56.520 --> 14:00.127
- We will take care of things here.
- Thank you.

14:00.200 --> 14:02.885
[Dad] Kids, we're going to a hotel.

14:02.960 --> 14:05.566
They don't know where it came from.

14:19.440 --> 14:23.525
<i>[TV announcer] Transportation
authorities have begun a search...</i>

14:23.600 --> 14:25.887
Frankie Feeder.

14:26.000 --> 14:28.287
<i>...no airline will claim...</i>

14:28.360 --> 14:30.408
You remember him?

14:31.360 --> 14:33.408
From high school.

14:34.800 --> 14:36.882
Hmm.

14:38.080 --> 14:40.128
He died.

14:42.360 --> 14:45.409
- On his way to the prom.
- Mm.

14:45.480 --> 14:47.562
- Remember?
- Mm-hm.

14:50.400 --> 14:52.448
They said he was doomed.

14:53.000 --> 14:55.128
Mm.

14:57.320 --> 14:59.402
Jesus.

15:00.560 --> 15:03.769
They could have said the same thing about Donnie.

15:05.440 --> 15:07.568
