15:08.320 --> 15:13.008
If it fell from a plane,
then what happened to the plane?

15:14.040 --> 15:16.771
They don't know, Samantha.

15:26.320 --> 15:30.882
Mrs. Farmer will bring you home after practice.
Bye, honey.

15:30.960 --> 15:33.645
Donnie. Good luck.

15:33.720 --> 15:36.246
Oh, my God. Tell me everything.

15:36.320 --> 15:39.290
- I'm not allowed to.
- Oh, my God.

15:40.040 --> 15:42.441
- Hi, Cherita.
- Shut up.

15:42.520 --> 15:45.046
Darko cheats death, uh?

15:45.120 --> 15:47.361
You're like a celebrity, man.

15:47.440 --> 15:49.681
I kept calling you. Where you been?

15:49.800 --> 15:51.643
We stayed at a hotel.

15:51.760 --> 15:55.685
My dad saw you at the golf course.
You sleepwalking again?

15:55.800 --> 16:01.170
- I don't wanna talk about it.
- Now you're famous, have a smoke.

16:04.680 --> 16:07.160
What happens if you tell Mom and Dad?

16:07.320 --> 16:10.164
You'll put Ariel in the garbage disposal.

16:10.280 --> 16:14.171
- Goddamn right I will.
- So grotty.

16:14.240 --> 16:16.925
Hey, Cherita. You want a cigarette?

16:17.000 --> 16:19.810
- Shut up!
- Shut up!

16:19.880 --> 16:22.121
Go back to China, bitch.

16:24.800 --> 16:26.689
Just leave her alone.

16:26.760 --> 16:28.330
Some good shit, huh?

16:29.080 --> 16:31.651
It's a fucking cigarette.

